94ce></path></svg> Monero</span><span class=\"payment-badge\" data-v-a32094ce><svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"23\" data-v-a32094ce></line><path d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\" data-v-a32094ce></path></svg> Cash</span></div></div></section><section class=\"trust-section\" data-v-a32094ce><div class=\"container\" data-v-a32094ce><div class=\"trust-grid\" data-v-a32094ce><div class=\"trust-content\" data-v-a32094ce><h2 data-v-a32094ce>Audited &amp; transparent</h2><div class=\"privacy-features\" data-v-a32094ce><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce><svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\" data-v-a32094ce></polyline></svg> No connection logs or session data retained</div><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce><svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\" data-v-a32094ce></polyline></svg> No customer information stored post-purchase</div><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce><svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\" data-v-a32094ce></polyline></svg> Annual third-party security audits (#7 completed May 2025)</div><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce><svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\" data-v-a32094ce></polyline></svg> Public transparency reports and warrant canary</div><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce><svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\" data-v-a32094ce></polyline></svg> Disclosed ownership and team with 15-year operating history</div><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce><svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\" data-v-a32094ce></polyline></svg> No affiliate program, no tracking scripts, no surveillance advertising</div></div><div class=\"limitations-box\" data-v-a32094ce><div class=\"grid-pattern\" data-v-a32094ce></div><div class=\"limitations-content\" data-v-a32094ce><p class=\"limitations-title\" data-v-a32094ce>Limitations we acknowledge</p><div class=\"privacy-features\" data-v-a32094ce><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce>We operate servers in 58 locations / 41 countries.</div><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce>We don&#39;t offer port forwarding.</div><div class=\"feature-item\" data-v-a32094ce>No streaming compatibility guarantees.</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"server-image\" data-v-a32094ce><img src=\"/images/02blue.png\" alt=\"Pixel art server rack infrastructure with blue accents showing internal components\" data-v-a32094ce></div></div></div></section><section class=\"cta-section\" data-v-a32094ce><div class=\"container\" data-v-a32094ce><div class=\"cta-content\" style=\"font-size:1.1rem;\" data-v-a32094ce><p data-v-a32094ce>If you&#39;ve read this far, you know what we&#39;re about.</p><p data-v-a32094ce>Choose the plan that matches your threat model.</p><button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-cta\" data-v-a32094ce><svg class=\"icon icon-up\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><polyline points=\"18 15 12 9 6 15\" data-v-a32094ce></polyline></svg> Select Plan <svg class=\"icon icon-up\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-v-a32094ce><polyline points=\"18 15 12 9 6 15\" data-v-a32094ce></polyline></svg></button></div></div></section></div></div></div></div>"}